    "concept_sort_game": "active တၢ်ဆိကမိၣ် sort တၢ်ဂဲၤလိၥ် interface လ၁် categorization practice. Drag အပှ into correct category buckets ဆူ demonstrate understanding အ classification concepts. Immediate feedback ဒုးနဲၣ် correct ဒီး incorrect placements. Supports 2-4 categories ဒီး any number အ sortable အပှ. ဒိၣ် လ၁် vocabulary tiers, science classifications, မ့တမ့် grammar sorting.",
